      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\displaystyle x_{k}=\mathrm {argmin} _{y\in \mathbb {R} ^{n}}{\left\{(x-y)^{\top }A(x-y):y\in \operatorname {span} \left\{b,Ab,\ldots ,A^{k-1}b\right\}\right\}}}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/be615f8ca25516092c1d7d611daf40f52bc1729d" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-display mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -1.171ex; width:66.348ex; height:3.509ex;" alt="{\displaystyle x_{k}=\mathrm {argmin} _{y\in \mathbb {R} ^{n}}{\left\{(x-y)^{\top }A(x-y):y\in \operatorname {span} \left\{b,Ab,\ldots ,A^{k-1}b\right\}\right\}}}"></span>The algorithm is detailed below for solving <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle \mathbf {A} \mathbf {x} =\mathbf {b} }">
