</p>
<div class="mw-heading mw-heading4"><h4 id="Explicit_residual_calculation">Explicit residual calculation</h4><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Conjugate_gradient_method&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6" title="Edit section: Explicit residual calculation"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
