Now, the rate of convergence can be approximated as <sup id="cite_ref-BP_4-3" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-BP-4"><span class="cite-bracket">[</span>4<span class="cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup><sup id="cite_ref-10" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-10"><span class="cite-bracket">[</span>10<span class="cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup>
